    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Class containing 3 orders, 61 genera, and 325 species of fungi, including rapidly-growing species, most of which are saprobes, plant pathogens, and mycoparasites, including those that induce human mycosis.</Note_Text>
